---
import CornellNote from '../../../components/CornellNote.astro';
---

<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<title>유형 05 - 난이도 [수능] 연습</title>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.css">
		<script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.js"></script>
		<script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/contrib/auto-render.min.js"></script>
		<style>
			body { background-color: #e0e0e0; margin: 0; padding: 20px; display: flex; justify-content: center; }
			.sol-button {
				display: inline-block; padding: 4px 12px; background: #ffebee; color: #c62828;
				border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: bold;
				margin-left: 10px; border: 1.5px solid #c62828; transition: all 0.2s ease;
				white-space: nowrap;
			}
			.sol-button:hover { background: #c62828; color: white; transform: translateY(-1px); }
			.question-card { background: white; padding: 25px; border-radius: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px; border: 1px solid #eee; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.02); }
			.question-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 15px; gap: 10px; }
			.formula-box { background: #fafafa; padding: 25px; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.8; }
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<CornellNote title="유형 05. 무리식 극한 [수능]" chapter="Level: CSAT">
			<div slot="cues">
				<p style="margin: 0; font-weight: bold; color: #1a1a1a;">🔴 [수능] 핵심 전략</p>
				<ul style="margin-top: 10px; padding-left: 18px; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.6; color: #444;">
					<li>극한이 존재하려면 분자도 반드시 { "$ 0 $" }이어야 합니다.</li>
					<li>유리화 후 남는 식에서 <b>미지 계수</b>를 결정합니다.</li>
					<li>두 극한 조건이 주어지면 <b>연립</b>하여 풉니다.</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<section>
				<div class="type-section">
					<p style="margin-bottom: 25px; color: #666;">유리화 기법과 극한의 존재 조건을 결합한 수능형 문항입니다.</p>

					<!-- Q1 -->
					<div class="question-card">
						<div class="question-header">
							<p style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.05rem;"><b>Q1.</b> 다음이 성립할 때, 상수 { "$ a $" }의 값을 구하시오.</p>
							<a href="/wiki/chapter01/solutions/type05-high/q1" class="sol-button">풀이 💡</a>
						</div>
						<div class="formula-box" style="text-align: center;">
							{ "$ \\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to 0} \\frac{\\sqrt{1+ax}-1}{x} = 2 $" }
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Q2 -->
					<div class="question-card">
						<div class="question-header">
							<p style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.05rem;"><b>Q2.</b> 다항함수 { "$ f(x) $" }에 대하여 { "$ f(4) = 0 $" }이고 다음이 성립할 때, { "$ \\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to 4} \\frac{f(x)}{x-4} $" }의 값을 구하시오.</p>
							<a href="/wiki/chapter01/solutions/type05-high/q2" class="sol-button">풀이 💡</a>
						</div>
						<div class="formula-box" style="text-align: center;">
							{ "$ \\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to 4} \\frac{f(x)}{\\sqrt{x}-2} = 6 $" }
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Q3 -->
					<div class="question-card">
						<div class="question-header">
							<p style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.05rem;"><b>Q3.</b> 상수 { "$ a, b $" }에 대하여 다음이 성립할 때, { "$ a + b $" }의 값을 구하시오.</p>
							<a href="/wiki/chapter01/solutions/type05-high/q3" class="sol-button">풀이 💡</a>
						</div>
						<div class="formula-box" style="text-align: center;">
							{ "$ \\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to 1} \\frac{\\sqrt{ax+b}-2}{x-1} = 3 $" }
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div style="margin-top: 40px; display: flex; gap: 15px;">
					<a href="/wiki/chapter01/types/type05/" style="color: #666; text-decoration: none;">← 핵심 문제로 이동</a>
					<a href="/wiki/chapter01/problems-const/" style="color: #666; text-decoration: none;">목록으로 돌아가기</a>
				</div>
			</section>
		</CornellNote>

		<script is:inline>
			if (typeof window !== 'undefined') {
				document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
					if (typeof renderMathInElement === 'function') {
						renderMathInElement(document.body, {
							delimiters: [
								{left: '$$', right: '$$', display: true},
								{left: '$', right: '$', display: false}
							],
							throwOnError : false
						});
					}
				});
			}
		</script>
	</body>
</html>
